          "text": "3. Bundle — one run with all items\n\nBundle passes the whole array. Combine Text joins them into a single string. For fields like generate-image.referenceImageUrls or combine-audio, Bundle lands as multiple inputs.\n\nFor a text combiner like this, Bundle and Each produce the same concatenation — the difference is execution count (1 vs 3).",
