          "text": "4. Item vs Selected\n\nItem is a fixed index — here 0, the first prompt. Even if you click a different result on the source, Item keeps picking index 0.\n\nSelected reads whichever result is currently active on the source node (click a result on the AI Agent carousel to change which one).",
